The paper deals with spoof detection in fingerprints, which is a problem in computer vision and image processing. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves machine learning techniques for classification, which falls under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper uses image synthesis techniques, which can be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
